comment: Global offset is -1.4 to compensate glass-supported homing procedure. GelMA (T1) and HAMA (T2). Vol. T1: 600 µL (layer 1), + 600 µL (layer 3). Vol. T2: 600 µL (layer 2).  Washing channels: dipping, then rinsing 5x0.6 mL warm DPBS with pipette, removing excess liquid with KimWipe (touching channels). Store in warm ECGM2 until further use.  Super prints except number 6 (airbuuble in first in last layer.  Transferring all at the same time into separate 24-wells with 0.5 mL 2x Hase in ECGM2 +P/S (230409 MF).
